Notes:
Discuss Cleverly's LinkedIn lead generation services for Dave Lancaster's home builder lending business at Builders Capital.
,  - Dave needs to generate leads for home builders to offer Builders Capital's lending services
  - Cleverly's "Gold" plan builds a targeted list, writes outreach sequences, automates outreach, and provides a dashboard for Dave to manage responses
  - The "Platinum" plan includes Cleverly managing all responses and booking meetings for Dave
  - Dave will start with the Gold plan and his daughter will manage responses using Cleverly's resources
  - Cleverly has techniques to find home builders on LinkedIn and follows best practices to avoid restrictions
,Builders Capital and Dave's Role

  - Builders Capital is the largest private lender to home builders in the US
  - Dave joined last September to grow their lending business in the Midwest/East as banks pull back
  - He needs to source home builder clients and make them aware of Builders Capital's lending services

Cleverly's LinkedIn Lead Gen Services

  - Cleverly builds a targeted list of prospects using LinkedIn Sales Navigator data
  - They write a 4-step outreach sequence and automate the initial outreach (connection requests, follow-ups)
  - Provides a dashboard for Dave/his team to manage responses that come in
  - Averages 125 connections accepted and 31 responses per 500 connection requests sent

Implementation Details

  - Dave will sign up for the Gold plan with 3-month commitment, then month-to-month
  - His daughter will manage responses using Cleverly's resources (response guides, templates, AI assistance)
  - Cleverly can segregate the new home builder contacts from Dave's existing network
  - 500 connection requests per month is a safe limit to avoid LinkedIn restrictions
  - Cleverly uses cloud automation, residential IPs, human-mimicking patterns to stay compliant
,  - Builders Capital is the largest private lender to home builders in the US
  - Dave joined last September...

Notes:
Discuss Cleverly's LinkedIn lead generation services for financial advisors
,  - Cleverly offers LinkedIn lead generation campaigns tailored for financial advisors
  - They build targeted prospect lists using LinkedIn Sales Navigator and send multi-step messaging sequences
  - Packages include Gold (client manages responses) and Platinum (Cleverly manages responses and books meetings)
  - Minimum 3-month commitment, then month-to-month with 10-day cancellation notice
,LinkedIn Lead Gen Process

  - Use LinkedIn Sales Navigator to build targeted prospect lists based on criteria like job title, location, company, experience
